{"tid":1082341,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[磚]一人一件屋企人做過最戅鳩嘅事","createTime":"2019-03-29T01:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T07:54:51.000Z","uid":198627,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dee49df8c86baf054c4fb2ffa1ca6d57606d6358","tid":1082341,"uid":198627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:41:19.000Z","msg":"事源我每次返到屋企都慣將個銀包擺喺門口個櫃上面 以便出門口攞<br />\n有一日準備出門口嘅時候發現唔見咗銀包<br />\n搵咗好耐都冇 最後打畀老母救命<br />\n佢一開頭話嗰朝出門口有見過 同我慢慢recap咗我放過喺邊 我話放過入外套袋之後佢就幾肯定咁話我一定跌咗 重講到勁嚴重<br />\n當下我就打算去報警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知過咗5分鐘之後 佢話佢唔小心攞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但明明我哋個銀包完全唔同色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢亦都冇漏低自己個銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：好愛老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c0a350920fcf45ba1bf34e1d80eb4ad36409bc","tid":1082341,"uid":73002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:46:00.000Z","msg":"老母同我拗法國喺意大利入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116e152955405f153d929d56d84dcdab8b5af76a","tid":1082341,"uid":45431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"10c0a350920fcf45ba1bf34e1d80eb4ad36409bc","tid":1082341,"uid":73002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:46:00.000Z","msg":"老母同我拗法國喺意大利入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:48:30.000Z","msg":"依啲有乜好拗，打開個地圖咪完<br />\n你嘥時間同佢拗你都有啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1792fd3b0d1590eff9d489d8533e77f1f80b625","tid":1082341,"